    "Courts need to assess whether insufficient user oversight qualifies as foreseeable misuse and whether the manufacturer should have taken steps to prevent it through product design, warnings, and marketing.",
    "Excessive trust in the safety of AI systems can lead to misuse, as users may overly rely on the AI's decisions.",
    "Users may not always know when to intervene, when AI systems seem to be operating within their designated parameters but require human intervention beyond their programming (Ramos & Mosleh, 2021, 3).",
